TITLE: Animating TripsLayer currentTime prop using popmotion in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet demonstrates how to animate the `currentTime` prop of a `TripsLayer` in deck.gl using the `popmotion` library. It initializes a `Deck` instance and defines an animation that updates the layer's `currentTime` property, triggering a layer update on each frame. The animation ranges from 0 to 1800 over 5 seconds, repeating indefinitely. Requires `@deck.gl/core`, `@deck.gl/geo-layers`, and `popmotion`.
