TITLE: Enabling Picking with ScatterplotLayer (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to enable picking for a ScatterplotLayer in TypeScript. It includes type definitions for the data and the picking info. The `pickable` prop is set to `true` and `onHover` and `onClick` callbacks are specified to handle hover and click events, logging the picking info and event details.
SOURCE: https://github.com/visgl/deck.gl/blob/master/docs/developer-guide/interactivity.md#_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
