TITLE: Using GridLayer with DeckGL React Component
DESCRIPTION: This React/TypeScript example demonstrates how to integrate the GridLayer within a React application using the DeckGL component. It defines the data type, creates the GridLayer instance, and renders the DeckGL component passing the layer and initial view state as props.
