TITLE: Rendering H3ClusterLayer in React with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to integrate the H3ClusterLayer within a React functional component using DeckGL. The data type is defined explicitly for typing props and interactions. The component initializes the layer with properties for hexagon retrieval, fill color, and line color, and renders the DeckGL component with view state and tooltip configurations. Required dependencies include React, @deck.gl/react, @deck.gl/core, and @deck.gl/geo-layers, and the component expects external H3 cluster JSON data served at the specified URL.
