TITLE: Updating Layer Props Imperatively with deck.setProps (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates the challenge of updating layer props imperatively using the standard `deck.setProps` method.  It requires repeating all existing props, which can be cumbersome when only a few properties need to be changed. This is especially problematic when data and previous props are no longer easily accessible in the current scope.
