TITLE: Proposed Implementation for PathLayer with Partial Updates
DESCRIPTION: Modified implementation for PathLayer that supports updating only a specified range of paths, demonstrating the approach for non-instanced attributes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/visgl/deck.gl/blob/master/dev-docs/RFCs/v7.2/partial-updates-rfc.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
calculateStartPositions( {value, start, end}) {
    const {paths} = this.state;
    for (let i = start; < end; ++i) {
         const path = this.state.paths[i]
         const numSegments = path.length - 1;
      for (let ptIndex = 0; ptIndex < numSegments; ptIndex++) {
        const point = path[ptIndex];
        value[i++] = point[0];
        value[i++] = point[1];
        value[i++] = point[2] || 0;
      }
    });
  }
```

